{"tid":2066894,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"明居正：總加速師feel到自己分分鐘玩撚完 所以要戰狼四圍出征","createTime":"2020-06-16T15:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T23:50:18.000Z","uid":58841,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"001c086542fcb47f19aa127adc5f18b2374afc5f","tid":2066894,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:08:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QnAWib1je54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQnAWib1je54&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=fca4ad29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QnAWib1je54</a><br />\n第一個就係佢講<br />\n由頭開始聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中国同美國雙方好大壓力 <br />\n中国主要問題<br />\n1反習派<br />\n2国安法<br />\n明居正仲講埋車臣係世界係極度負面既案例<br />\n張曉明咁講引黎國際強烈既反應 係咪意思你諗住血腥鎮壓香港人<br />\n<br />\n美國主要問題<br />\n國內經濟<br />\n連任<br />\n<br />\n你有壓力 我有壓力 所以Hawaii見面唔會傾得一次<br />\n台面上主要傾<br />\n1 港版国安法<br />\n2貿易協議<br />\n3台海問題<br />\n4武漢肺炎問題<br />\n5新疆法案問題<br />\n如果傾得成既話下次可能就係彭斯同王歧山出黎傾<br />\n對美國黎講其實制裁香港係殺敵一萬自損八千<br />\n<br />\n後半段自己聽埋佢<br />\n總之就係話維尼有滅頂危機 所以會加強国安法<br />\n香港人日子會過得更加難過<br />\n同時會四圍挑機顯得自己好強大"},{"pid":"f488336e73796b5bd89027bcb2cb60c0ac7ed265","tid":2066894,"uid":263618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:09:04.000Z","msg":"所以我咪話有得食沙律就好食沙律"},{"pid":"593fd68467e66023e098c0a638e67f72c65b3da4","tid":2066894,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"傾唔成最好"},{"pid":"a25c41341ce2a6c65933d3fe7a5b4256e21bd6b0","tid":2066894,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"593fd68467e66023e098c0a638e67f72c65b3da4","tid":2066894,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"傾唔成最好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"對香港人黎講梗係最好傾唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"